    "communications_language": "en_US",
    "description": "Padel Montenegro is the first padel club in Montenegro, located in Donja Lastva near Tivat (close to Hotel Kamelija). It features 2 outdoor padel courts and offers padel court bookings, equipment sales (Head rackets, balls), and table tennis. The club was founded by former professional water polo players Damjan Danilović and Vjekoslav Pasković, who aim to promote padel as a fun and accessible sport for all ages and skill levels. The club also imports and assembles padel courts across Montenegro. Reservations can be made via phone, email, or the Taykus booking platform."
  },
