    "communications_language": "en_US",
    "description": "Luštica Bay Padel Courts are located in the Centrale neighbourhood of the luxurious Luštica Bay resort on the Luštica Peninsula in Montenegro, near Tivat. The two outdoor padel courts sit within the vibrant Piazza Centrale — a modern Mediterranean town centre surrounded by restaurants, shops, and residential buildings. The courts offer beautiful coastal and mountain views and are part of a larger sports complex that includes tennis, basketball, beach volleyball, and bocce. The padel courts have hosted international tournaments, including a FIP Promotion event in 2024. Court bookings can be made online via the Luštica Bay reservation system at €25 per court. The resort is approximately 12 km from Tivat Airport, 62 km from Dubrovnik Airport, and 92 km from Podgorica Airport."
  },
