    "communications_language": "en_US",
    "description": "Porto Montenegro Sports Club's padel court offers the fastest growing sport in the world within the luxurious Porto Montenegro resort in Tivat, on the Bay of Kotor. The padel court is available for booking by residents, marina guests, crew, and the local community. Social matches and professional coaching sessions are available for all skill levels, with equipment rental included in the price. The court is part of a larger sports complex that also features tennis courts, a squash court, fitness suite, bowling alley, and more. Bookings are made via email (scbookings@portomontenegro.com) or phone (+382 32 660 744)."
