    "communications_language": "en_US",
    "description": "Olive Padel Court at Maestral Resort & Casino is a premium padel destination nestled along Montenegro's stunning Adriatic coast, right beside the sea and surrounded by ancient olive trees in the town of Pržno, near Sveti Stefan. The facility features 2 state-of-the-art outdoor padel courts operated in partnership with Olive Padel Club. Open daily from 08:00 to midnight, the courts are playable all year round thanks to Montenegro's mild coastal climate. The venue has already hosted two editions of the Adriatic Padel Cup (in partnership with the Vibe Padel Tour), attracting international players and guests. The courts cater to all skill levels — beginners can take private lessons and rent equipment, while advanced players can join competitive games. As part of the 5-star Maestral Resort, guests also enjoy access to fine dining, a world-class spa & wellness center, private beach, casino, and other resort amenities. Free parking is available, along with a bar/restaurant, showers, and free Wi-Fi."
  },
