    "communications_language": "en_US",
    "description": "Platinum Padel Centar Budva is a premier padel destination located in the heart of Budva on Slovenska Plaža (Slovenska Beach), within the popular Slovenska Plaža Resort. Spanning 3,000 m², it features 7 top-quality Padel Galis courts (3 indoor and 3 outdoor, plus additional courts) with professional lighting for day and night play. The club offers private coaching, a padel school for all levels, and a café bar where players can relax after a match with panoramic views of the surrounding area. It regularly hosts national tournaments and club events, catering to both locals and tourists. The club is open to all skill levels – from beginners to advanced players."
