    "description": "Splendid Padel & Tennis Club is part of the 5-star Splendid Conference & SPA Resort in Bečići, Budva, Montenegro. Set right by the Adriatic Sea, it features two brand-new JUBO padel courts and one US Open style hard tennis court, all surrounded by Mediterranean gardens and sea views. Open to hotel guests, locals, and tourists alike, the club offers equipment rental, certified coaching, and a full resort experience including restaurants, bars, a large SPA, gym, and private beach. Pricing for padel: €28–€32 for 55 min (depending on time slot)."
