    "description": "Padel Titograd Tereni (Donja Gorica) is a padel club in the Donja Gorica suburb of Podgorica, Montenegro. It was among the first padel courts opened in Podgorica. The club features 3 modern padel courts and is open daily from 9 AM to 10 PM. Facilities include a café/bar with a view of the courts, a padel equipment shop, changing rooms, and free private parking. Rackets and balls are provided for players, making it accessible to beginners. The club also offers professional instruction and has hosted tournaments, summer leagues, and children's padel schools."
  },
