    "communications_language": "en_US",
    "description": "PADEL Club Bar is a newly opened padel facility located on the promenade (šetalište) in Bar, Montenegro, within the SRC Topolica sports complex. Opened in August 2025 in partnership with the Sportsko-rekreativni centar Bar and operated by brothers Dušan and Darko Bigović (PADEL CLUB DOO), it features 3 outdoor padel courts and an on-site caffe bar. The club is open daily from 8 AM to midnight. Court reservations can be made via Instagram DM or WhatsApp, or through the ZakaziTermin app. The club also runs a weekend league (@padel.league.bar). Rackets are included in the court rental price (from €30/hour)."
  },
