    "communications_language": "en_US",
    "description": "The SRC Bar Padel Courts at Topolica are Montenegro's newest padel facility, officially opened in April 2026 on the grounds of the Sportsko-rekreativni centar Bar (SRC Bar) in the Madžarica area. The project was realized in partnership with brothers Dušan and Darko Bigović. The two double outdoor padel courts are part of a larger sports complex that already includes football fields, tennis courts, an indoor gym, and the modern Topolica Sports Hall (capacity 2,625). The courts are floodlit for evening play. A separate but related Padel Club Bar operates 3 additional padel courts on the city promenade (šetalište) with extended hours (8 AM – midnight) and its own café bar. Together, these facilities mark the arrival of padel as a major new sport in Bar, described by SRC director Božidar Janković as 'the beginning of a new sports era' for the city."
  },
