    "communications_language": "en_US",
    "description": "Sportski Centar Igalo is a large multi-sport complex in Igalo, Herceg Novi, Montenegro. Its padel court – the first ever in Herceg Novi – opened in August 2025 and features a synthetic surface with LED lighting for day and night play. The court is built to FIP (World Padel Federation) standards and is suitable for both recreational and competitive matches. The wider sports centre also offers football, tennis (3 clay courts), beach volleyball (3 sand courts), basketball, a multi-purpose indoor hall, a gym, and the Hotel Play with a restaurant. The complex covers 4,200 m² with a 2,995 m² indoor sports hall."
  },
