    "description": "Padel Montenegro (Padel klub Tivat) is the first padel club in Montenegro, established in 2021. Located in Donja Lastva, Tivat, near Hotel Kamelija, it features a total of 7 premium courts (4 indoor and 3 outdoor) with glass walls and high-quality lighting. The club is the official distributor of HEAD and Babolat padel equipment in Montenegro and offers table tennis facilities, a pro shop, and coaching services with professional trainer Luka Petranović. Open daily from 7 AM to 12:30 AM, it provides free parking and organizes tournaments, children's padel schools, and social events for the local padel community."
