    "description": "Padel klub Budva (commercially known as Platinum Padel Centar Budva) is a padel sports club located on Slovenska Beach (Slovenska Plaža) in the heart of Budva, Montenegro. Registered with the Padel Federation of Montenegro (Padel Savez Crne Gore), the club opened in 2023 and features a total of six courts — three indoor and three outdoor — equipped with premium Jubo Padel Infinity courts. The facility includes an on-site café with indoor and outdoor seating, shower and changing facilities, and offers private coaching and regular tournament events. Set among pine trees near the Adriatic coast, the club provides a scenic and professional padel experience for players of all levels."
